</h3>
<p>
    The best time to catch chum salmon near Gresham is between <strong>late October and early December</strong>. This window aligns with their spawning season when they travel upstream in large numbers. Mornings after a fresh rainfall often produce the best action.
</p>
<h3>
    <strong>Ideal Weather Conditions</strong>
</h3>
<p>
